      <p>
        Oncall claims are divided into <b>passive</b>, <b>activated passive</b> and <b>active</b> calls.
        <br><br>
        <b>Passive</b>: You are oncall, but you only clocked less than 4 hours of work in the hospital. <br>
        <b>Claim: Weekday RM80, Weekend RM90</b><br><br>
        <b>Activated Passive</b>: You are oncall and clocked equal or more than 4 hours of work in the hospital.<br>
        <b>Claim: Weekday RM120, Weekend RM130</b><br><br>
        <b>Active</b>: You are oncall and will be staying in the hospital for 24 hours. - only done by 4th year
        students<br>
        <b>Claim: Weekday RM200, Weekend RM220</b><br><br>

        Make sure to submit your claim within <b>90</b>days from your oncall months, or you will have a lot more trouble
        claiming
        it later. You can access your claim site from the <a href="http://my.ummc.edu.my/" target="_blank">main hospital
